 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:32:47.000Z","msg":"冇乜理 功能組別 嗰邊<br />\n<br />\n自由黨投反對，有幾大影響？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:34:07.000Z","msg":"政府議案係咪唔駛分組點票?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"政府嘢應該係過半就得，但係咪啲議員修訂要好似要2邊"},{"pid":"e5d37a031e479fe7cd912695d3f065c45324d86f","tid":1095502,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:40:49.000Z","msg":"大田你仲邊有影響力呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c57134121f014dc3da0bd138a2d928c44e91ea0","tid":1095502,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:46:19.000Z","msg":"唔明點解行政會議成員就唔可以反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前長者津貼上調去到65歲孽瘤都反對啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}